{"id":32,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":32,"title":"D&C 28","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 28"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet to Oliver Cowdery, at Fayette, New York, September 1830. Hiram Page, a member of the Church, had a certain stone and professed to be receiving revelations by its aid concerning the upbuilding of Zion and the order of the Church. Several members had been deceived by these claims, and even Oliver Cowdery was wrongly influenced thereby. Just prior to an appointed conference, the Prophet inquired earnestly of the Lord concerning the matter, and this revelation followed."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.1-7"},"1–7"],", Joseph Smith holds the keys of the mysteries, and only he receives revelations for the Church;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.8-10"},"8–10"],", Oliver Cowdery is to preach to the Lamanites;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.11-16"},"11–16"],", Satan deceived Hiram Page and gave him false revelations."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.1","order":"06.05.028.3359"},["b","1"],"Behold, I say unto thee,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Oliver"],", that it shall be given unto thee that thou shalt be heard by the church in all things whatsoever thou shalt teach them by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Comforter"],", concerning the revelations and commandments which I have given."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.2","order":"06.05.028.3360"},["b","2"],"But, behold, verily, verily, I say unto thee,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"no one"],"shall be appointed to receive commandments and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"revelations"],"in this church excepting my servant",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"Joseph Smith, Jun."],", for he receiveth them even as",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"Moses"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.3","order":"06.05.028.3361"},["b","3"],"And thou shalt be obedient unto the things which I shall give unto him, even as",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Aaron"],", to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"declare"],"faithfully the commandments and the revelations, with power and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"authority"],"unto the church."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.4","order":"06.05.028.3362"},["b","4"],"And if thou art",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"led"],"at any time by the Comforter to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"speak"],"or teach, or at all times by the way of commandment unto the church, thou mayest do it."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.5","order":"06.05.028.3363"},["b","5"],"But thou shalt not write by way of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"commandment"],", but by wisdom;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.6","order":"06.05.028.3364"},["b","6"],"And thou shalt not command him who is at thy head, and at the head of the church;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.7","order":"06.05.028.3365"},["b","7"],"For I have given him the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"keys"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"mysteries"],", and the revelations which are sealed, until I shall appoint unto them another in his stead."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.8","order":"06.05.028.3366"},["b","8"],"And now, behold, I say unto you that you shall go unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Lamanites"],"and preach my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"gospel"],"unto them; and inasmuch as they",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"receive"],"thy teachings thou shalt cause my",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"church"],"to be established among them; and thou shalt have revelations, but write them not by way of commandment."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.9","order":"06.05.028.3367"},["b","9"],"And now, behold, I say unto you that it is not revealed, and no man knoweth where the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"city"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"Zion"],"shall be built, but it shall be given hereafter. Behold, I say unto you that it shall be on the borders by the Lamanites."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.10","order":"06.05.028.3368"},["b","10"],"Thou shalt not leave this place until after the conference; and my servant Joseph shall be appointed to preside over the conference by the voice of it, and what he saith to thee thou shalt tell."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.11","order":"06.05.028.3369"},["b","11"],"And again, thou shalt take thy brother, Hiram Page,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"between"],"him and thee alone, and tell him that those things which he hath written from that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"stone"],"are not of me and that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"Satan"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"deceiveth"],"him;"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.12","order":"06.05.028.3370"},["b","12"],"For, behold, these things have not been appointed unto him, neither shall anything be appointed unto any of this church contrary to the church covenants."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.13","order":"06.05.028.3371"},["b","13"],"For all things must be done in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"order"],", and by common",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"consent"],"in the church, by the prayer of faith."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.14","order":"06.05.028.3372"},["b","14"],"And thou shalt assist to settle all these things, according to the covenants of the church, before thou shalt take thy journey among the Lamanites."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.15","order":"06.05.028.3373"},["b","15"],"And it shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"given"],"thee from the time thou shalt go, until the time thou shalt return, what thou shalt do."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.16","order":"06.05.028.3374"},["b","16"],"And thou must open thy mouth at all times, declaring my gospel with the sound of rejoicing. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.1a","order":"06.05.028.3375"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.3.3,38"},"D&C 20:3 (3, 38)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.1b","order":"06.05.028.3377"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-comforter"},"TG Holy Ghost, Comforter"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teaching-with-the-spirit"},"Teaching with the Spirit"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.2a","order":"06.05.028.3379"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/32.4"},"D&C 32:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.17.17-18"},"35:17 (17–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.4"},"43:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/order"},"Order"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.2b","order":"06.05.028.3381"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.2c","order":"06.05.028.3383"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.15.14-20"},"2 Ne. 3:15 (14–20)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/joseph-smith"},"TG Joseph Smith"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.2d","order":"06.05.028.3385"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/1.1"},"Lev. 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.3a","order":"06.05.028.3387"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/4.30.14-16,30"},"Ex. 4:30 (14–16, 30)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/28.1.1-5"},"28:1 (1–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.3b","order":"06.05.028.3389"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/26.2"},"Jer. 26:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.3c","order":"06.05.028.3391"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-authority"},"TG Priesthood, Authority"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.4a","order":"06.05.028.3393"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/5.18"},"Gal. 5:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.4b","order":"06.05.028.3395"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/4.12.12-16"},"Ex. 4:12 (12–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/24.6.5-6"},"D&C 24:6 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.8.8,32"},"Moses 6:8 (8, 32)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.5a","order":"06.05.028.3397"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.5"},"D&C 43:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.22.22-23"},"63:22 (22–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.7a","order":"06.05.028.3399"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.18"},"D&C 35:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.5"},"64:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.19"},"84:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-keys-of"},"TG Priesthood, Keys of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.7b","order":"06.05.028.3401"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mysteries-of-godliness"},"TG Mysteries of Godliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.8a","order":"06.05.028.3403"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.19.18-22"},"2 Ne. 3:19 (18–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/17.1"},"Alma 17:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/30.5"},"D&C 30:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/32.2.1-3"},"32:2 (1–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.24"},"49:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.8b","order":"06.05.028.3405"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.20"},"D&C 3:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.8c","order":"06.05.028.3407"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teachable"},"TG Teachable"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.8d","order":"06.05.028.3409"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/13.6.6-10"},"Ether 13:6 (6–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.9a","order":"06.05.028.3411"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.2"},"D&C 57:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.24.22-24"},"103:24 (22–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.9b","order":"06.05.028.3413"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52.42.42-43"},"D&C 52:42 (42–43)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.11a","order":"06.05.028.3415"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/18.15"},"Matt. 18:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.11b","order":"06.05.028.3417"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorcery"},"TG Sorcery"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/superstitions"},"Superstitions"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.11c","order":"06.05.028.3419"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/20.10"},"Rev. 20:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.4"},"D&C 50:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.11d","order":"06.05.028.3421"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.6.5-7"},"D&C 43:6 (5–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7"},"46:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.13a","order":"06.05.028.3423"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/order"},"TG Order"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.13b","order":"06.05.028.3425"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/common-consent"},"TG Common Consent"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/28.15a","order":"06.05.028.3427"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32.5.3,5"},"2 Ne. 32:5 (3, 5)"],"."]]}
